Recommended rooms 

Discover our curated selection of rooms, chosen to match the style and size of your celebration.

Main Hall

100-200 guests

3200 sq ft

High ceilings, marble pillars, and towering drapes frame this elegant space — perfect for weddings, galas, and large events.

Jasmine Cellar

20-40 guests

600 sq ft

High ceilings, warm brick arches, and cozy lighting define this inviting cellar — ideal for private dinners and cocktail receptions.

Lotus Lounge

20-50 guests

700 sq ft

A sleek space with bamboo accents, custom lighting, and a private bar — great for intimate and upscale gatherings.

Amenities

Enhance your event with our in-house offerings — available for an additional fee.

80" Smart TV Screen

80" smart TV screen for visuals and media playback.

Valet Parking

Professional valet service for guest convenience.

Full-Size LED Wall

Floor-to-ceiling LED wall for custom visuals or branding.

90" Smart TV Screen

Large 90" smart TV screen for presentations or media.

Wireless & Podium Microphones

Handheld and podium microphones for speeches or music.

Full-Service Bar

Includes bartender and full setup for beverage service.

Professional Services

Through our trusted partners, we can assist in arranging premium external services by request.

Photo Booth

Interactive booth with props, backdrops, and instant prints.

Themed Decor & Styling

Custom event styling based on your theme or celebration.

Lighting Engineer

Expert lighting setup for atmosphere, spotlighting, and shows.

DJ Services

Live DJ with curated playlists and crowd engagement.

Event Host / MC

Keep the event flowing smoothly with a charismatic on-site host.

Photographer / Videographer

Capture every moment with professional photo and video coverage.
